metadata.name: Drip For Good #1847
metadata.description:
Drip for Good is a collection of 6,000 unique H2Omie NFTs â€” digital collectibles living on the Ethereum blockchain. Your H2omie is on a mission to bring clean accessible water to those in the most remote regions of the world. Your H2Omie doubles as your GoodPASS, and grants you access to members-only benefits, the first of which is access to our Giving Hand, a community fund for members in need. Together with our digital H2Omies, we can help end the World Water Crisis by bringing clean water to the 771 million people that struggle to find it daily.

  Drip for Good is the first collection released by Just for Good, and targets the World Water Crisis.
